### 11.2 文件上传

**POST /api/v1/upload/chunk**

请求（multipart/form-data）
```
fileMd5=5f4dcc3b5aa765d61d8327deb882cf99
chunkIndex=0
totalSize=10485760
fileName=manual.pdf
totalChunks=2
orgTag=PRIVATE_alice
isPublic=false
file=<binary>
```

响应
```json
{
  "code": 200,
  "message": "分片上传成功",
  "data": {
    "uploaded": [0],
    "progress": 50.0
  }
}
```

**GET /api/v1/upload/status**

请求
```
/api/v1/upload/status?file_md5=5f4dcc3b5aa765d61d8327deb882cf99
```

响应
```json
{
  "code": 200,
  "message": "获取上传状态成功",
  "data": {
    "uploaded": [0,1],
    "progress": 100.0,
    "fileName": "manual.pdf",
    "fileType": "PDF文档"
  }
}
```

**POST /api/v1/upload/merge**

请求
```json
{
  "fileMd5": "5f4dcc3b5aa765d61d8327deb882cf99",
  "fileName": "manual.pdf"
}
```

响应
```json
{
  "code": 200,
  "message": "文件合并成功，任务已发送到 Kafka",
  "data": {
    "object_url": "https://minio.example.com/uploads/merged/manual.pdf?X-Amz-..."
  }
}
```

**GET /api/v1/upload/supported-types**

响应
```json
{
  "code": 200,
  "message": "获取支持的文件类型成功",
  "data": {
    "supportedTypes": ["PDF文档", "Word文档", "Markdown文档"],
    "supportedExtensions": ["pdf", "docx", "md"],
    "description": "系统支持的文档类型文件，可被解析并进行向量化处理"
  }
}
```

