### 11.5 对话与 WebSocket

**GET /api/v1/chat/websocket-token**

响应
```json
{
  "code": 200,
  "message": "获取WebSocket停止指令Token成功",
  "data": {"cmdToken": "WSS_STOP_CMD_123456"}
}
```

**WebSocket /chat/{token}**

客户端发送
```json
"请总结这个文档的重点"
```

服务端流式返回
```json
{"chunk":"该文档主要包含..."}
```

完成通知
```json
{"type":"completion","status":"finished","message":"响应已完成","timestamp":1711330000000,"date":"2026-03-25T08:30:00"}
```

停止指令（携带内部 token）
```json
{"type":"stop","_internal_cmd_token":"WSS_STOP_CMD_123456"}
```

