### 11.4 检索与解析

**GET /api/v1/search/hybrid**

请求
```
/api/v1/search/hybrid?query=知识库&topK=5
```

响应
```json
{
  "code": 200,
  "message": "success",
  "data": [
    {
      "fileMd5": "...",
      "chunkId": 1,
      "textContent": "...",
      "score": 0.92,
      "userId": "alice",
      "orgTag": "PRIVATE_alice",
      "public": false,
      "fileName": "manual.pdf"
    }
  ]
}
```

**POST /api/v1/parse**

请求（multipart/form-data）
```
file=<binary>
file_md5=5f4dcc3b5aa765d61d8327deb882cf99
```

响应
```
文档解析成功
```

