- Maven 3.8.6+
- MySQL 8
- Redis 7.x
- Elasticsearch 8.10.0
- Kafka 3.2.1
- MinIO 8.5.12

**前端环境**
- Node.js 18.20.0+
- pnpm 8.7.0+

