## 16. SQL DDL（建表语句）

说明：以下 DDL 基于实体注解推导，字段长度与索引可按实际数据库进行调整。

```sql
CREATE TABLE `users` (
  `id` BIGINT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `username` VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  `password` VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  `role` VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
  `org_tags` VARCHAR(1024) DEFAULT NULL,
  `primary_org` VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `uk_users_username` (`username`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `organization_tags` (
  `tag_id` VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  `name` VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  `description` TEXT,
  `parent_tag` VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` BIGINT NOT NULL,
  `created_at` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`tag_id`),
  KEY `idx_org_tags_parent` (`parent_tag`),
  CONSTRAINT `fk_org_tags_created_by` FOREIGN KEY (`created_by`) REFERENCES `users` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `file_upload` (
  `id` BIGINT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `file_md5` VARCHAR(32) NOT NULL,
  `file_name` VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_size` BIGINT DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` INT DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_id` VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
  `org_tag` VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_public` TINYINT(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `created_at` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  `merged_at` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `idx_file_upload_md5` (`file_md5`),
  KEY `idx_file_upload_user` (`user_id`),
  KEY `idx_file_upload_org` (`org_tag`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `document_vectors` (
  `vector_id` BIGINT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `file_md5` VARCHAR(32) NOT NULL,
  `chunk_id` INT NOT NULL,
  `text_content` LONGTEXT,
  `model_version` VARCHAR(32) DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_id` VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
  `org_tag` VARCHAR(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_public` TINYINT(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  PRIMARY KEY (`vector_id`),
  KEY `idx_doc_vectors_file` (`file_md5`),
  KEY `idx_doc_vectors_user` (`user_id`),
  KEY `idx_doc_vectors_org` (`org_tag`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `chunk_info` (
  `id` BIGINT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `file_md5` VARCHAR(32) NOT NULL,
  `chunk_index` INT NOT NULL,
  `chunk_md5` VARCHAR(32) DEFAULT NULL,
  `storage_path` VARCHAR(512) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `idx_chunk_file` (`file_md5`),
  KEY `idx_chunk_file_index` (`file_md5`, `chunk_index`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `conversations` (
  `id` BIGINT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user_id` BIGINT NOT NULL,
  `question` TEXT NOT NULL,
  `answer` TEXT NOT NULL,
  `timestamp` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `idx_user_id` (`user_id`),
  KEY `idx_timestamp` (`timestamp`),
  CONSTRAINT `fk_conversations_user` FOREIGN KEY (`user_id`) REFERENCES `users` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
```

 | 不得形成环 |

---

## 18. SQL 索引优化建议

- `users`
  - 已有 `username` 唯一索引，建议新增 `role` 索引以优化按角色筛选。
- `organization_tags`
  - `parent_tag` 与 `created_by` 索引用于树查询与审计。
- `file_upload`
  - 建议索引：`(file_md5, user_id)`、`(file_name, is_public)`、`(org_tag, is_public)`、`(user_id, status)`。
  - 说明：下载/预览按 `file_name` 与 `is_public` 查询，组织过滤按 `org_tag`。
- `document_vectors`
  - 建议索引：`(file_md5, chunk_id)`、`(user_id, org_tag, is_public)`。
- `chunk_info`
  - 建议唯一索引：`(file_md5, chunk_index)` 防止重复分片。
- `conversations`
  - 已有 `user_id`、`timestamp` 索引，建议组合索引 `(user_id, timestamp)`。

---

## 19. 更严格的 DDL（含外键级联策略）

说明：以下 DDL 在保持当前字段结构的前提下，增加可落地的外键与级联规则。`file_upload.user_id` 为字符串，`document_vectors/chunk_info` 仅保存 `file_md5`，因此无法建立严格外键；如需更强约束，需改为数值型 `user_id` 并在子表增加 `file_upload_id`。

```sql
CREATE TABLE `users` (
  `id` BIGINT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `username` VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  `password` VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  `role` VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
  `org_tags` VARCHAR(1024) DEFAULT NULL,
  `primary_org` VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `uk_users_username` (`username`),
  KEY `idx_users_role` (`role`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `organization_tags` (
  `tag_id` VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  `name` VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  `description` TEXT,
  `parent_tag` VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` BIGINT NOT NULL,
  `created_at` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`tag_id`),
  KEY `idx_org_tags_parent` (`parent_tag`),
  KEY `idx_org_tags_created_by` (`created_by`),
  CONSTRAINT `fk_org_tags_created_by`
    FOREIGN KEY (`created_by`) REFERENCES `users` (`id`)
    ON DELETE RESTRICT ON UPDATE CASCADE,
  CONSTRAINT `fk_org_tags_parent`
    FOREIGN KEY (`parent_tag`) REFERENCES `organization_tags` (`tag_id`)
    ON DELETE SET NULL ON UPDATE CASCADE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `file_upload` (
  `id` BIGINT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `file_md5` VARCHAR(32) NOT NULL,
  `file_name` VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_size` BIGINT DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` INT DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_id` VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
  `org_tag` VARCHAR(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_public` TINYINT(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  `created_at` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  `merged_at` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `idx_file_upload_md5_user` (`file_md5`, `user_id`),
  KEY `idx_file_upload_name_public` (`file_name`, `is_public`),
  KEY `idx_file_upload_org_public` (`org_tag`, `is_public`),
  KEY `idx_file_upload_user_status` (`user_id`, `status`),
  CONSTRAINT `fk_file_upload_org_tag`
    FOREIGN KEY (`org_tag`) REFERENCES `organization_tags` (`tag_id`)
    ON DELETE SET NULL ON UPDATE CASCADE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `document_vectors` (
  `vector_id` BIGINT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `file_md5` VARCHAR(32) NOT NULL,
  `chunk_id` INT NOT NULL,
  `text_content` LONGTEXT,
  `model_version` VARCHAR(32) DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_id` VARCHAR(64) NOT NULL,
  `org_tag` VARCHAR(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_public` TINYINT(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0,
  PRIMARY KEY (`vector_id`),
  KEY `idx_doc_vectors_file_chunk` (`file_md5`, `chunk_id`),
  KEY `idx_doc_vectors_user_org_public` (`user_id`, `org_tag`, `is_public`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `chunk_info` (
  `id` BIGINT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `file_md5` VARCHAR(32) NOT NULL,
  `chunk_index` INT NOT NULL,
  `chunk_md5` VARCHAR(32) DEFAULT NULL,
  `storage_path` VARCHAR(512) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `uk_chunk_file_index` (`file_md5`, `chunk_index`),
  KEY `idx_chunk_file` (`file_md5`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;

CREATE TABLE `conversations` (
  `id` BIGINT NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user_id` BIGINT NOT NULL,
  `question` TEXT NOT NULL,
  `answer` TEXT NOT NULL,
  `timestamp` DATETIME DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `idx_conversations_user_time` (`user_id`, `timestamp`),
  CONSTRAINT `fk_conversations_user`
    FOREIGN KEY (`user_id`) REFERENCES `users` (`id`)
    ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4;
```

**可选升级方案（更强外键）**
- 将 `file_upload.user_id` 改为 `BIGINT` 外键指向 `users.id`。
- 在 `document_vectors` 与 `chunk_info` 增加 `file_upload_id` 外键，替代 `file_md5` 关联。
- 这样可对文档相关数据使用 `ON DELETE CASCADE`，彻底避免孤儿记录。

## 20. 按模块拆分的请求参数字典

说明：按功能模块汇总请求参数，字段约束详见第 14 与第 17 节。

**20.1 认证与用户模块**

- 注册 `POST /api/v1/users/register`
  - `username` (Body, string, 必填)
  - `password` (Body, string, 必填)
- 登录 `POST /api/v1/users/login`
  - `username` (Body, string, 必填)
  - `password` (Body, string, 必填)
- 刷新 Token `POST /api/v1/auth/refreshToken`
  - `refreshToken` (Body, string, 必填)
- 当前用户 `GET /api/v1/users/me`
  - `Authorization` (Header, Bearer Token, 必填)
- 用户组织标签 `GET /api/v1/users/org-tags`
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 设置主组织 `PUT /api/v1/users/primary-org`
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
  - `primaryOrg` (Body, string, 必填)
- 上传组织标签 `GET /api/v1/users/upload-orgs`
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 登出 `POST /api/v1/users/logout`
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 全设备登出 `POST /api/v1/users/logout-all`
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)

**20.2 文件上传模块**

- 分片上传 `POST /api/v1/upload/chunk`
  - `fileMd5` (Form, string, 必填)
  - `chunkIndex` (Form, int, 必填)
  - `totalSize` (Form, long, 必填)
  - `fileName` (Form, string, 必填)
  - `totalChunks` (Form, int, 选填)
  - `orgTag` (Form, string, 选填)
  - `isPublic` (Form, boolean, 选填)
  - `file` (Form, file, 必填)
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 上传状态 `GET /api/v1/upload/status`
  - `file_md5` (Query, string, 必填)
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 合并分片 `POST /api/v1/upload/merge`
  - `fileMd5` (Body, string, 必填)
  - `fileName` (Body, string, 必填)
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 支持类型 `GET /api/v1/upload/supported-types`
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)

**20.3 文档管理模块**

- 删除文档 `DELETE /api/v1/documents/{fileMd5}`
  - `fileMd5` (Path, string, 必填)
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 可访问文档 `GET /api/v1/documents/accessible`
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 用户上传文档 `GET /api/v1/documents/uploads`
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 下载 `GET /api/v1/documents/download`
  - `fileName` (Query, string, 必填)
  - `token` (Query, string, 选填)
- 预览 `GET /api/v1/documents/preview`
  - `fileName` (Query, string, 必填)
  - `token` (Query, string, 选填)

**20.4 检索与解析模块**

- 混合检索 `GET /api/v1/search/hybrid`
  - `query` (Query, string, 必填)
  - `topK` (Query, int, 选填)
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 文档解析 `POST /api/v1/parse`
  - `file` (Form, file, 必填)
  - `file_md5` (Form, string, 必填)
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)

**20.5 对话模块**

- WebSocket 停止指令 token `GET /api/v1/chat/websocket-token`
  - 无参数
- WebSocket 连接 `/chat/{token}`
  - `token` (Path, string, 必填)
  - `message` (WS Text, string/JSON, 必填)

**20.6 管理后台模块（ADMIN）**

- 用户列表 `GET /api/v1/admin/users`
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 添加知识 `POST /api/v1/admin/knowledge/add`
  - `file` (Form, file, 必填)
  - `description` (Form, string, 必填)
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 删除知识 `DELETE /api/v1/admin/knowledge/{documentId}`
  - `documentId` (Path, string, 必填)
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 系统状态 `GET /api/v1/admin/system/status`
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 用户活动 `GET /api/v1/admin/user-activities`
  - `username` (Query, string, 选填)
  - `start_date` (Query, string, 选填)
  - `end_date` (Query, string, 选填)
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 创建管理员 `POST /api/v1/admin/users/create-admin`
  - `username` (Body, string, 必填)
  - `password` (Body, string, 必填)
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 组织标签管理
  - `POST /api/v1/admin/org-tags`
    - `tagId` (Body, string, 必填)
    - `name` (Body, string, 必填)
    - `description` (Body, string, 选填)
    - `parentTag` (Body, string, 选填)
    - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
  - `GET /api/v1/admin/org-tags`
    - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
  - `GET /api/v1/admin/org-tags/tree`
    - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
  - `PUT /api/v1/admin/org-tags/{tagId}`
    - `tagId` (Path, string, 必填)
    - `name` (Body, string, 选填)
    - `description` (Body, string, 选填)
    - `parentTag` (Body, string, 选填)
    - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
  - `DELETE /api/v1/admin/org-tags/{tagId}`
    - `tagId` (Path, string, 必填)
    - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 用户标签分配 `PUT /api/v1/admin/users/{userId}/org-tags`
  - `userId` (Path, long, 必填)
  - `orgTags` (Body, string[], 必填)
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 用户分页 `GET /api/v1/admin/users/list`
  - `keyword` (Query, string, 选填)
  - `orgTag` (Query, string, 选填)
  - `status` (Query, int, 选填)
  - `page` (Query, int, 选填)
  - `size` (Query, int, 选填)
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)
- 对话记录 `GET /api/v1/admin/conversation`
  - `userid` (Query, string, 选填)
  - `start_date` (Query, string, 选填)
  - `end_date` (Query, string, 选填)
  - `Authorization` (Header, 必填)

---

## 21. API 版本化策略

**目标**：在保证兼容性的前提下支持新特性与演进。

**策略建议**
- URL 版本前缀：保持 `/api/v1/...` 形式，新版本使用 `/api/v2/...`。
- 版本升级时：
  - 兼容性变更使用新版本路径。
  - 小幅字段扩展保持向后兼容，可在 v1 中追加字段并保持默认值。
- Deprecation 规则：
  - 在响应头中增加 `Deprecation` 与 `Sunset`（时间戳）提示。
  - 文档中标记即将废弃接口与替代接口。
- 版本切换策略：
  - 前端通过配置 `VITE_SERVICE_BASE_URL` 指向目标版本。
  - 后端按版本分包维护控制器（如 `controller.v1`、`controller.v2`）。

**示例**
- 现有：`/api/v1/documents/preview`
- 新版：`/api/v2/documents/preview`（新增字段 `previewType`）

---

## 22. 数据库迁移脚本

建议使用 Flyway（或 Liquibase）。以下为 Flyway 示例结构：

```
/db/migration/
  V1__init_schema.sql
  V2__add_indexes.sql
  V3__add_constraints.sql
```

**V1__init_schema.sql**（初始建表）
```sql
-- 基础表结构（与第 16/19 节一致）
-- users, organization_tags, file_upload, document_vectors, chunk_info, conversations
```

**V2__add_indexes.sql**（索引优化）
```sql
CREATE INDEX idx_users_role ON users(role);
CREATE INDEX idx_file_upload_md5_user ON file_upload(file_md5, user_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_file_upload_name_public ON file_upload(file_name, is_public);
CREATE INDEX idx_file_upload_org_public ON file_upload(org_tag, is_public);
CREATE INDEX idx_file_upload_user_status ON file_upload(user_id, status);
CREATE INDEX idx_doc_vectors_file_chunk ON document_vectors(file_md5, chunk_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_doc_vectors_user_org_public ON document_vectors(user_id, org_tag, is_public);
CREATE UNIQUE INDEX uk_chunk_file_index ON chunk_info(file_md5, chunk_index);
CREATE INDEX idx_conversations_user_time ON conversations(user_id, timestamp);
```

**V3__add_constraints.sql**（外键与级联）
```sql
ALTER TABLE organization_tags
  ADD CONSTRAINT fk_org_tags_created_by
  FOREIGN KEY (created_by) REFERENCES users(id)
  ON DELETE RESTRICT ON UPDATE CASCADE;

ALTER TABLE organization_tags
  ADD CONSTRAINT fk_org_tags_parent
  FOREIGN KEY (parent_tag) REFERENCES organization_tags(tag_id)
  ON DELETE SET NULL ON UPDATE CASCADE;

ALTER TABLE file_upload
  ADD CONSTRAINT fk_file_upload_org_tag
  FOREIGN KEY (org_tag) REFERENCES organization_tags(tag_id)
  ON DELETE SET NULL ON UPDATE CASCADE;

ALTER TABLE conversations
  ADD CONSTRAINT fk_conversations_user
  FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id)
  ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE;
```

**迁移执行**
- Flyway 自动执行：应用启动时检测 `db/migration` 目录。
- 手动执行：按 `V1 -> V2 -> V3` 顺序执行。

（文档完）



